===從軍===
巴西隆在軍旅生涯展開之前，曾在地方的一家鄉間俱樂部當球童。之後他加入美國陸軍<ref name="Brady"></ref>{{rp|p80}}，赴菲律賓完成3年[[駐外美軍|海外役期]]，並在部隊中成為[[拳擊|拳擊]]比賽冠軍<ref>[[美國參議院|U.S. Senate]].  [http://www.gpo.gov/fdsys/pkg/CREC-2005-11-18/pdf/CREC-2005-11-18-pt1-PgS13334-2.pdf "Congressional Record"] {{WebCite|url=https://www.webcitation.org/610OOzWTX?url=http://www.gpo.gov/fdsys/pkg/CREC-2005-11-18/pdf/CREC-2005-11-18-pt1-PgS13334-2.pdf |date=20110817123644 |dateformat=iso }}, November 18, 2005, S13334-5.  Accessed on September 02, 2010.</ref>。他在一開始入伍時是分派到{{Link-en|傑伊堡|Fort Jay}}的{{Link-en|美國陸軍第16步兵團|16th Infantry Regiment (United States)|第16步兵團}}，但後來改調至{{Link-en|美國陸軍第31步兵團|31st Infantry Regiment (United States)|第31步兵團}}<ref>{{cite book |last=Tatum |first=Chuck |title=Red Blood, Black Sand: Fighting Alongside John Basilone from Boot Camp to Iwo Jima |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=hX2CgJkYFN0C&pg=PT66&dq=John+Basilone+%2216th+Infantry%22&hl=en&sa=X&ei=-vcgUdvEH6GE2gXh2IDoDg&ved=0CDMQ6AEwAQ#v=onepage&q=John%20Basilone%20%2231st%20Infantry%22&f=false |accessdate=2013-02-17 |year=2012 |publisher=Penguin |isbn=9781101585061 |page=66 |archive-date=2014-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140629165328/http://books.google.com/books?id=hX2CgJkYFN0C&pg=PT66&dq=John+Basilone+%2216th+Infantry%22&hl=en&sa=X&ei=-vcgUdvEH6GE2gXh2IDoDg&ved=0CDMQ6AEwAQ#v=onepage&q=John%20Basilone%20%2231st%20Infantry%22&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Alexander |first1=Colonel Joseph H. |year=2010 |title=Real Marines Behind HBO's The Pacific |journal={{Link-en|海軍歷史雜誌|Naval History (magazine)|Naval History}} |volume=24 |issue=2 |pages=26–27 |publisher={{Link-en|美國海軍學會|United States Naval Institute|United States Naval Institute}} |url=http://www.mydigitalpublication.com/publication/?i=32367&p=28 |accessdate=2013-02-17 |archive-date=2014-03-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140312212023/http://www.mydigitalpublication.com/publication/?i=32367&p=28 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。從陸軍退役後的巴西隆到[[馬里蘭州|馬里蘭州]]的{{Link-en|雷斯特斯鎮 (馬里蘭州)|Reisterstown, Maryland|雷斯特斯鎮}}開貨車謀生<ref name="pacificwrecks">{{cite web|url=http://pacificwrecks.com/valor/moh/basilone/|title=Gy/Sgt John Basilone, Medal of Honor|publisher=Pacific Wrecks|accessdate=2014-03-14|archive-date=2014-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140314165158/http://pacificwrecks.com/valor/moh/basilone/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。當了幾個月的貨運司機後，巴西隆想回到自己在陸軍服役時待過的[[馬尼拉|馬尼拉]]，並且認為加入海軍陸戰隊的話，能比陸軍更快調到那裡，於是他在1940年7月，到[[巴爾的摩|巴爾的摩]]向陸戰隊報到，在{{Link-en|帕里斯島海軍陸戰隊新兵訓練基地|Marine Corps Recruit Depot Parris Island|帕里斯島基地}}完成了新兵訓練後，又至[[匡提科海軍陸戰隊基地|匡提科基地]]和{{Link-en|新河海軍陸戰隊航空基地|Marine Corps Air Station New River|新河航空基地}}參加進階訓練。接著，軍方將巴西隆送到關塔那摩灣去等待後續派遣，然後他便歸入[[美國第1海軍陸戰師|第1陸戰師]]{{Link-en|美國第7海軍陸戰團|7th Marine Regiment (United States)|第7團}}{{Link-en|美國海軍陸戰隊第7團第1營|1st Battalion 7th Marines|第1營}}的D連，準備前往[[索羅門群島|索羅門群島]]中的瓜達康納爾作戰<ref name="pacificwrecks"></ref>。

====瓜達康納爾島====
