{{Link-en|橋水-拉瑞騰高中|Bridgewater-Raritan High School}}內的足球場命名為「巴西隆球場」（{{lang|en|Basilone Field}}），場邊的附樓上也有描繪他的壁畫；哥倫布騎士會（{{lang|en|Knights of Columbus Council}}）的13264號支社亦以巴西隆命名<ref name>{{Cite book |accessdate=2014-03-12 |title=John Basilone: World War II Medal of Honor Recipient for Action in the Pacific |author=McCaulay, Philip Martin |isbn=978-0-557-34574-8 |publisher=Lulu.com |year=2010}}</ref>{{rp|p37}}。

在紐澤西州，202號公路橫越{{Link-en|桑莫維爾圓環|Somerville Circle}}和206號公路上方的[[陸橋|陸橋]]稱作巴西隆陸橋。該州的[[拉瑞騰河|拉瑞騰河]]上也有兩座名為巴西隆的橋梁，一座是[[紐澤西收費高速公路|紐澤西收費高速公路]]的{{Link-en|巴西隆橋|Basilone Bridge}}<ref name=findagrave>{{Find a Grave|19842|work=Claim to Fame: Medal of Honor recipients|accessdate=2007-10-21}}</ref>，另一座是較晚興建的{{Link-en|約翰·巴西隆老兵紀念大橋|John Basilone Veterans Memorial Bridge}}。

在巴西隆的老家拉瑞騰境內，於舊約克路（{{lang|en|Old York Road}}）和運河街（{{lang|en|Canal Street}}）交叉口設置了一座巴西隆雕像，雕像的手中扛著白朗寧機槍，雕刻師正是巴西隆的幼時好友菲力普·奧蘭多（{{lang|en|Phillip Orlando}}）。[[華盛頓特區|華盛頓特區]]的{{Link-en|美國海軍紀念廣場|United States Navy Memorial}}也為巴西隆立匾<ref name=MacGillis>{{Cite news |accessdate=2010-02-25 |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2006/05/28/AR2006052801090.html |title=Honoring One Marine To Remember Them All: WWII Hero Gets Plaque at Navy Memorial |author=MacGillis, Alec |date=2006-05-29 |page=B01 |work=Washington Post |archive-date=2012-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121111115024/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2006/05/28/AR2006052801090.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在聖地牙哥小義大利區內的松樹街（{{lang|en|Fir Street}}）和印度街（{{lang|en|India Streets}}）街口同樣設有巴西隆的半身雕像，而當地為了紀念加入美軍、參與二戰和[[韓戰|韓戰]]的義大利裔居民所建的廣場，也取名作巴西隆廣場（{{lang|it|Piazza Basilone}}）<ref name=piazza>{{Cite web |accessdate=2010-08-19 |url=http://www.littleitalysd.com/points-of-interest/piazza-basilone/ |title=Piazza Basilone |publisher=The Little Italy Association |date= |archive-date=2011-08-17 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/610OUzWV5?url=http://www.littleitalysd.com/points-of-interest/piazza-basilone/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在美義大利之子組織（{{lang|en|Order Sons of Italy In America}}）設在紐約[[长岛_(纽约)|長島]]{{Link-en|波希米亞 (紐約州)|Bohemia, New York|波希米亞}}的2442號支社以巴西隆命名<ref>{{Cite web|accessdate=2010-02-26 |url=http://www.osia2442.org/ |title=Sgt. John Basilone Lodge 2442 - OSIA |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100128230104/http://www.osia2442.org/ |archivedate=2010-01-28}}</ref>。拉瑞騰公共圖書館（{{lang|en|Raritan Public Library}}）設有「巴西隆室」（{{lang|en|Basilone Room}}），展示並收藏他的相關紀念品<ref name="Brady"></ref>{{rp|p84}}。

====遊行====
拉瑞騰自1981年起，都會在其境內的桑莫塞街（{{lang|en|Somerset Street}}）舉辦紀念巴西隆的遊行，該慶典到後來成了一項敦親睦鄰的社區性活動<ref>{{Citation   | last = Eugene   | first = Paik   | title = Annual John Basilone Parade stirs feelings of patriotism, Jersey pride   | newspaper = The Star-Ledger   | date = Spetmber 25, 2011   | url = http://www.nj.com/news/index.ssf/2011/09/annual_john_basilone_parade_st.html   | accessdate = 2011-09-25   | quote =    | archive-date = 2011-10-03   | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20111003214318/http://www.nj.com/news/index.ssf/2011/09/annual_john_basilone_parade_st.html   | dead-url = no   }}</ref>。

